Album: Strength of a WomanArtist: Mary J. BligeGenre: R&amp;B/Soul/Hip hopRelease: April 28Mary J Blige's 13th studio album explores her troublesome marriage and divorce with estranged husband Martin Kendu Isaacs. It features guest appearances from Kanye West, Quavo, DJ Khaled and Missy Elliot. Essential tracks on the 14 track album include "Love Yourself," "Thick of It," "Smile" and "Strength of a Woman'. Mary J. Blige is brilliance. This feels like an effort only she can put together. Instead of shying away from her problems, she turns them into an empowering record.Star rating: 3.5